Windows Doctor is a comprehensive and reliable utility that can help you easily protect, maintain and optimize your system, repair your registry entries and diagnose problems that the low performance of your computer. Windows Doctor offers an all-in-one for maintenance and daily protection for your PC.

Windows Doctor combines 14 essential and practical tools for Windows so that, with a few mouse clicks, you can fix registry errors, clean privacy, prevent security threats, temporary Windows specific files, manage startups, recover lost data, split / shred files, repair Windows, speed up the system and more.

These utilities help users clean up garbage information from the registry, protect their privacy, make their PC run faster and with better performance.
